CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776708665
OL,3,CWill Labour lose its grip on power in
OL,4,Cthe Welsh election?
OL,6,FAmong his generation, Jeff says there
OL,7,Fis a growing feeling that the "good
OL,8,Ftimes" they had enjoyed would never
OL,9,Freturn.
OL,11,F"They are all worried about the
OL,12,Ffuture. Not for themselves...but for
OL,13,Four grandsons and granddaughters.
OL,15,F"What are my grandsons going to do
OL,16,Fnow?" he asked. "All the people in the
OL,17,Fvalleys want is employment, a good
OL,18,Feducation, and a good health service."
OL,26,@pD@FO]sD@AOUwD@AOUxD@EO]xD@QOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
