OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776708665
OL,3,CWill Labour lose its grip on power in
OL,4,Cthe Welsh election?
OL,6,FOthers in Merthyr Tydfil spoke of a
OL,7,Fdisappointment with Labour, mixed with
OL,8,Fa broader apathy. While a few
OL,9,Findicated they may stick with Labour,
OL,10,Fother lifelong Labour voters suggested
OL,11,Fthey might not vote at all.
OL,13,FFurther west in Tonna, near the
OL,14,Fwestern end of the Heads of the
OL,15,FValleys road, Sonny Singh has recently
OL,16,Fopened his first shop. He is hopeful
OL,17,Ffor the future, but thinks something
OL,18,Fneeds to change.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776708665
OL,3,CWill Labour lose its grip on power in
OL,4,Cthe Welsh election?
OL,6,FThe rise in the price of petrol is
OL,7,Fbiting especially hard in communities
OL,8,Fwhere driving is often a necessity.
OL,10,FSingh did not want to discuss party
OL,11,Fpolitics, but said many of his
OL,12,Fcustomers are fed up with politicians
OL,13,Fwho fail to keep their promises.
OL,15,FWhat we heard from voters along the
OL,16,FHeads of the Valleys is what makes
OL,17,FProfessor of Public Policy and
OL,18,FGovernance at Cardiff University,
OL,19,FLaura McAllister, believe this may be
OL,20,Fabout more than a difficult election
OL,21,Ffor Labour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
