CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776708665
OL,3,CWill Labour lose its grip on power in
OL,4,Cthe Welsh election?
OL,6,FBut Labour should not be "written
OL,7,Foff", according to Professor
OL,8,FMcAllister.
OL,10,FResearch by Cardiff University
OL,11,Fsuggests the party has the longest
OL,12,Fwinning streak of any political party
OL,13,Fin the world.
OL,15,FSince the party won the most seats and
OL,16,Fvotes at the 1922 General Election,
OL,17,FLabour has never lost a major election
OL,18,Fin its political birthplace. For some,
OL,19,Fthat loyalty runs very deep.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUoD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
