OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776708665
OL,3,CWill Labour lose its grip on power in
OL,4,Cthe Welsh election?
OL,6,FTravelling the Heads of the Valleys,
OL,7,Fthe physical legacy of the Labour
OL,8,Fmovement is everywhere: statues,
OL,9,Fminers' institutes, and murals.
OL,11,FWhat feels less certain is whether the
OL,12,Femotional connection between party and
OL,13,Fplace still carries the force it once
OL,14,Fdid.
OL,16,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,17,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,18,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,19,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
